ddf.catalog.impl

Class QueryResponsePostProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • ddf.catalog.impl.QueryResponsePostProcessor

  • public class QueryResponsePostProcessor
extends Object
    Class called by the catalog framework after all the results have been received from the different federated sources, before any of the post-query plug-ins are called. The current implementation adds the Metacard.RESOURCE_DOWNLOAD_URL attribute to all the Metacard objects contained in the QueryResponse. The download URL is generated using the ActionProvider whose ID is "catalog.data.metacard.resource".

      • processResponse

        public void processResponse(QueryResponse queryResponse)
        Performs any required post-processing on the QueryResponse object provided.

        This implementation converts the resource URIs found in the QueryResponse Metacards using the ActionProvider injected in the constructor.

        Parameters:
        queryResponse - QueryResponse to process. Cannot be null.
